  "detailed_description": "<h1>CHECK OUT OTHER GAMES</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704310/extras/02c04a0c2c0e818b583f7d8242e167b2.avif?t=1766123662\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br>After being summoned by Zafir to the world of Burning Horns, Diego, a firefighter student from São Paulo, see himself in a magical realm. In this place, humans and humanoid beings, such as elves, satyrs, and merfolk, have always experienced free love without prejudice among equals. However, today these people struggle to maintain their lifestyle and survive the threat posed by Onoob Asrol, a realm-riding demon who wants to turn everyone against the kingdom, and his shadows.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704310/extras/6f5afb71e82114d56baab4b4a0b6ee99.avif?t=1766123662\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic JRPG;<br></li><li>Unique playable characters;<br></li><li>Level up system;<br></li><li>Party system;<br></li><li>Immersive world;<br></li><li>An adventure in which Diego learns spells from his rainbow insignia;</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704310/extras/4d2a532bb1facf62801f1be6ef725fdb.avif?t=1766123662\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704310/extras/f988a96f37d60aad2bb482f5bc08d578.avif?t=1766123662\" width=600 height=452 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704310/extras/b2caf6795a0652f2ad41eb132db7c633.avif?t=1766123662\" width=600 height=452 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704310/extras/788fa93e2e5c4411b37c2a54974dfb6d.avif?t=1766123662\" width=600 height=452 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704310/extras/c2813b5f585b177bf82cd19f456ae3f5.avif?t=1766123662\" width=600 height=452 /></span>",
